      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>University of Oulu</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      During last years topical steroid creams have been suggested to be effective treatment for
      non-retractable foreskin instead of circumcision.

      Aim of this study is to investigate the efficacy, safety and persistence of treatment results
      of a medium potent steroid cream in a double-blind, randomized, placebo-controlled study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
